provisions.content:
Il-Kors ikun offrut fl-oqsma ta’ speċjalizzazzjoni li ġejjin:
Clinical Psychology, Counselling Psychology, Educational Psychology,
Forensic Psychology, Health Psychology, u Neuropsychology.

Rekwiżiti għaddħul.
